query:
SELECT 
  p.id AS projeto_id,
  p.nome AS projeto_nome,
  COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS total_clientes,
  COUNT(DISTINCT m.id) AS total_mercados,
  COUNT(DISTINCT co.id) AS total_concorrentes,
  COUNT(DISTINCT l.id) AS total_leads
FROM projects p
LEFT JOIN clientes c ON c.projectId = p.id
LEFT JOIN mercados_unicos m ON m.projectId = p.id
LEFT JOIN concorrentes co ON co.projectId = p.id
LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.projectId = p.id
WHERE p.nome LIKE '%Jeep%'
GROUP BY p.id
ORDER BY p.id DESC
LIMIT 1;
